        <header level="1">Sub-Machine Guns</header>
        <text>   Sub-Machine guns are generally sized between Medium and Large, and are chambered in a pistol caliber, such as 9x19mm or .40 S&amp;W. Sub-machine guns are created with a fixed stock. When crafting a weapon with automatic fire, the creator can choose what rate of fire the automatic fires at.
        </text>
